      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Great opportunity for buyers seeking a dependable, well-maintained vehicle! This car is in good condition \u2014 it runs reliably, presents well, and is ready for daily driving without the headaches of a project car. You'll find it's been looked after and offers the kind of solid, everyday performance you can count on. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
