    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "A fantastic opportunity for the budget-savvy buyer or hands-on DIY enthusiast! We want to be upfront with you \u2014 this vehicle is in poor condition and shows significant wear both inside and out. It has mechanical issues and cosmetic imperfections that reflect its age and use, so it's best suited for someone comfortable with repairs or looking for a project car. That said, it's a real chance to get behind the wheel at a price that won't break the bank \u2014 perfect for basic transportation needs or a fun fixer-upper!",
