    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in mint condition, and we are genuinely proud to present it. The exterior is absolutely stunning \u2014 the paint retains its original deep luster with zero scratches, chips, or blemishes of any kind. Every panel is straight and true, the glass is crystal clear, and all trim pieces are intact and gleaming. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs with remarkable smoothness and responsiveness. The interior is equally impressive: the upholstery shows no wear, fading, or staining, all controls and electronics function perfectly, and the cabin retains a fresh, well-cared-for feel. The tires have excellent tread depth remaining, the brakes are in top shape, and the vehicle has been serviced regularly. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that truly lives up to the 'mint' designation \u2014 a car you can drive with confidence and pride from day one.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a poor-condition car, best suited for buyers who are comfortable with a significant project or are looking for a parts vehicle. The exterior shows substantial wear, including multiple dents, deep scratches, rust spots, and noticeably faded or peeling paint in several areas. The interior is worn throughout \u2014 expect torn or heavily stained upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and a general sense of neglect. Mechanically, the car has known issues that will require meaningful repair work before it can be considered fully reliable for regular daily driving; buyers should budget for repairs beyond the purchase price. There are no recent service records to speak of, and the vehicle is sold as-is. That said, at this price point, it represents an honest opportunity for the right buyer \u2014 a skilled DIY mechanic, a restoration enthusiast, or someone in need of specific components. Please inspect thoroughly before purchasing.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition, and we're committed to giving you a complete and honest picture before you make any decisions. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains good gloss and color consistency across most panels, though there are a few minor scratches and small stone chips consistent with normal road use. There are no significant dents or structural damage to report. The interior is clean and well-maintained; upholstery shows only light wear on the driver's seat and door panels, and all major surfaces are free of tears or heavy staining. The dashboard, controls, and infotainment system are all functional. Mechanically, the vehicle runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts promptly, idles smoothly, and delivers solid performance during driving. Brakes, steering, and suspension all feel responsive and appropriate for the mileage. Tires have reasonable tread remaining, though replacement may be needed within the next year or two depending on your driving habits. All major electrical systems \u2014 lights, windows, locks, and climate control \u2014 are in working order. This is a solid, dependable vehicle that has been reasonably cared for and is ready for its next owner without requiring immediate major repairs.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
